room_title: Escape room "Captured Comrades" by Blue Ops Mission in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Great escape room experience! Loved that you controlled when you wanted a clue vs the host giving you clues at their leisure as other escape rooms sometimes do. Will be coming back to escape from the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Captured Comrades" by Blue Ops Mission in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Captured ComradesPlace is great! Super friendly and well put together scenarios! It was so good we went twice in one week!

room_title: Escape room "Captured Comrades" by Blue Ops Mission in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We had so much FUN in Captured Comrades for my husband's birthday. Great family escape from our regular weekend.
